data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value:
Hit the dice as many times as you can before times runs out. You have 15 seconds in each level. Every time you hit the dice your score will increase by the number of the dice. Please keep in mind that if you close the application your score will not be saved.
Level 1 (Beginner): Every one second the dice changes location in the red panel.
Level 2 (Intermediate): Every one second the dice changes location in the red panel, but be careful! If you miss the dice and your score minus the number of the dice is bigger than zero, your score will decrease by the number of the dice. If it is less than zero, your score will become zero. Where's the fun in that? Well, if you don't miss the dice, your score will be doubled in the end! Also, not every dice has the same size.
Level 3 (Legend): Are you up for a challenge? Every half a second the dice changes location in the red panel, but be careful! If you miss the dice and your score minus the number of the dice is bigger than zero, your score will decrease by the number of the dice. If it is less than zero, your score will become zero. Where's the fun in that? Well, if you don't miss the dice, your score will be doubled in the end! Also, the dice's size gets smaller the first 2 times you hit it.
